name: transferrin receptor
synonyms: CD71|TFR1|p90|LOC105374300|TFRC|transferrin receptor|TRANSFERRIN RECEPTOR; TFRC|K06503 transferrin receptor |(RefSeq) TFRC|TFR|T9|IMD46|p90|transferrin receptor|TRFR|TR
description: This gene encodes a cell surface receptor necessary for cellular iron uptake by the process of receptor-mediated endocytosis. This receptor is required for erythropoiesis and neurologic development. Multiple alternatively spliced variants have been identified.
